{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","data":{"alias":"external-convulsant-tomtit","description":"## Reproduction Steps\n\nThe `prompt-eval` GitHub Actions workflow runs the offline eval-discipline gate over\nevery packaged eval spec: it loads each `src/rebar/llm/eval_specs/*.eval.yaml` and calls\n`rebar.llm.evals.eval.validate_eval_spec(spec, strict=True)` for any dataset-bearing spec,\nasserting no errors.\n\n1. On `origin/main` (HEAD abdf44ef7), run the strict validator over the packaged specs.\n2. `plan-review-g7.eval.yaml` (added in ef4d5217d) carries a `dataset` but no `gold_set`.\n3. Strict validation returns `['strict: eval spec needs a non-empty gold_set (judge kappa alignment)']`,\n   the CI step asserts and exits 1 -> the `prompt-eval` job is red on main.\n\n**Expected:** every packaged dataset-bearing eval spec passes strict validation; `prompt-eval` green.\n**Actual:** `plan-review-g7.eval.yaml` fails strict validation for a missing `gold_set`.\n\n## Scope\n\nOnly `src/rebar/llm/eval_specs/plan-review-g7.eval.yaml`. Add a non-empty, balanced\n`gold_set` of `{input, label}` human-gold entries (label in `finding`/`pass`) for the G7\nleaf-parent-containment criterion, matching the convention used by\n`plan-review-container.eval.yaml`. No code changes.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] `plan-review-g7.eval.yaml` has a non-empty `gold_set`; each entry has an `input` and a `label` (`finding`|`pass`).\n- [ ] The gold_set is balanced (at least one `finding` and at least one `pass` gold label), mirroring the G7 fire/pass scenarios.\n- [ ] `validate_eval_spec(spec, strict=True)` returns `[]` (no errors) for the spec.\n- [ ] The `prompt-eval` offline discipline gate passes over all packaged specs (`make lint`/`make test` remain green).","id":"1e80-5f27-9c7b-418c","parent_id":"","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"bug","title":"prompt-eval CI red on main: plan-review-g7.eval.yaml missing gold_set"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783973696898422001,"uuid":"2cb4805e-afb9-4462-a52e-55254cfd54dd"}